\\mbox{\\textit{\\textbf{Soluzione 2.22}}
\\\\
\\;
\\\\Siano $A$ aperto in $R^n$, $B$ aperto in $R^m$,
\\\\$g \\in C^k(A)$, $f \\in C^k(B; R^n)$, tale
\\\\che $f(B) \\subseteq A$.
\\\\\\;
\\\\Allora $g \\circ f \\in C^k(B)
}
